(4. Why Steve Kerr Stayed With the Warriors) Tj
T*
(Source: Daring Fireball | Published: 2026-05-24T17:27:24Z) Tj
T*
(Link: https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/48686303/steve-kerr-decision-return-coach-golden-stat) Tj
T*
(e-warriors-steph-curry) Tj
T*
(Terrific, poignant profile of Warriors head coach Steve Kerr by Wright Thompson for ESPN: Kerr) Tj
T*
(doesn?t want the Warriors to end up like the New England Patriots, marred by grudges and) Tj
T*
(grievances. He watched Michael Jordan retire, then unretire, then retire, then unretire. His) Tj
T*
(friends used to grill him about MJ. ?Why doesn?t he go out on top?? ?Because he can?t,? Kerr) Tj
T*
(told them. For the past few years, Kerr has watched his mentor, San Antonio Spurs coach Gregg) Tj
T*
(Popovich, struggle through this same decision. Pop once called Steve to tell him he?d finally) Tj
T*
(decided to retire. Steve congratulated him on a Hall of Fame career. A week later Pop signed an) Tj
T*
(extension with San Antonio. Popovich finally officially quit six weeks before our lunch, six) Tj
T*
(months after a stroke diminished him physically. People who loved him had to show him the door,) Tj
T*
(as gently as possible. That hurt Steve. He respects Popovich so much. He loved playing for him) Tj
T*
(and coaching with him. He once told Gregg he was the finest man he?d ever known and thanked him) Tj
T*
(for all he?d done for him. Pop smiled and said his feet were made of clay like everyone else?s.) Tj
T*
(Steve didn?t believe it then. Now he does. ?I realized he couldn?t do...) Tj
T*
() Tj
